# Food Share Platform

## 1. Layout

* **Navbar:**

  * Not logged in → Logo, Home, Available Foods, Login
  * Logged in → Logo, Home, Available Foods, Add Food, Manage My Foods, My Food Requests, Profile, Logout
* **Footer:** Logo, copyright, social links

## 2. Home Page

* Banner + button
* Featured Foods: top 6 by quantity
* Show All button
* 2 static sections (How it Works, Mission)

## 3. Authentication(Firebase)

* Register: name, email, photoURL, password (upper, lower, 6 chars)
* Login: email, password
* Google login on both pages

## 4. Food CRUD (MongoDB)

* **Add Food (Private):** form + imgbb upload, auto donor info, status=Available
* **Available Foods (Public):** show only Available, View Details (login required)
* **Food Details (Private):** full info + Request Food button
* **Manage My Foods (Private):** user’s foods, update, delete

## 5. Food Request System

* Request Modal: location, reason, contact
* Save with status=pending
* Food Owner sees request table: Accept → status=accepted & food donated, Reject → rejected

## 6. Others

* Loading spinner
* 404 page
* Home animations (framer-motion)
